WEBVTT

00:03:58.066 --> 00:04:00.136
They can also feel the pain.

00:04:00.160 --> 00:04:03.576
This is called "phantom limbs"
in neuroscience.

00:04:03.600 --> 00:04:06.320
Neuroscience tells us that the mind,

00:04:06.320 --> 00:04:11.520
at every moment, continuously draws
a map of the body

00:04:11.520 --> 00:04:17.776
that we feel, even though at times
this map is wrong.

00:04:17.800 --> 00:04:23.216
So this body that we feel,
is a creation of the mind.

00:04:23.240 --> 00:04:26.136
Another example would be

00:04:26.160 --> 00:04:30.656
people suffering from mental state
like Schizophrenia